@base = http://localhost:8000/api

### Quick score entry (under 5 seconds — score + tag only)
POST {{base}}/journal/quick
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "score": 7,
  "tag": "positive",
  "date": "2026-04-04"
}

### Create entry with morning mode
POST {{base}}/journal
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Morning intention",
  "date": "2026-04-04",
  "score": 5,
  "tag": "positive",
  "entryMode": "morning"
}

### Create entry with evening mode
POST {{base}}/journal
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Evening review",
  "date": "2026-04-04",
  "score": 7,
  "tag": "positive",
  "entryMode": "evening"
}
